    PanelPRO-11

    PanelPRO11.Rd

    Runs PanelPRO with 11 genes (genes = c("BRCA1", "BRCA2", "ATM", "PALB2", "CHEK2", "EPCAM", "PMS2", "MLH1", "MSH2", "MSH6", "CDKN2A")) and 11 cancers (cancers = c("Brain", "Breast", "Colorectal", "Contralateral", "Endometrial", "Gastric", "Kidney", "Melanoma", "Ovarian", "Pancreas", "Prostate", "Small intestine")), as in PanelPRO:::MODELPARAMS$PanPRO11.

    PanelPRO11(...)

    Arguments

    ...

    Additional arguments to be passed into PanelPRO.

    See also

    PanelPRO

    Other predefined: BRCAPRO5(), BRCAPRO6(), BRCAPRO(), MMRPRO(), PanelPRO22()

    Examples

    data(test_fam_3)
PanelPRO11(test_fam_3, parallel = FALSE)
